{"tid":1919211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急]我喺YouTube畀班戇鳩仔起底, 仲畀佢地屈藍絲；Discord巴絲立即查下fd list有無可疑ac","createTime":"2020-03-10T15:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-05T07:18:28.000Z","uid":264529,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"daad939a1921f21f3e26ecc933cbb933de5daffa","tid":1919211,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">如果巴絲有玩Minecraft 同有discord ac, 請立即search下有無可疑人物。更加唔好接啲突如其來fd request</span><br />\n頭盔：呢個指控唔係為左分化，但佢地明知我係黃都用左對付狗嘅方式嚟攪鳩我<br />\n是咁的：兩年前有班人蝦我創作差, 我乞求教嘅時候，佢地玩玩下嘅心態令我攪唔掂，然後我封口同block左佢地嘅時候, 以為可以平息件事, 結果佢地用盡一切嘅手段, 仲開埋分身攪鳩我<br />\n其一：cap我荒廢左嘅ig就吹我係中國人(當時的確係，但已經修正)<br />\n其二：用分身喺我YouTube Channel dislike <a href=\"http://youtube.com/RBLXlottery248\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutube.com%2FRBLXlottery248&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=c9eae8b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">youtube.com/RBLXlottery248</a><br />\n三：將私人恩怨擺上公眾場合， 例(我條片)：<a href=\"https://youtu.be/BVNMr9bRuVo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FBVNMr9bRuVo&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=39eee249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/BVNMr9bRuVo</a> scroll去中後段嘅chat同往後comment<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n關鍵名：<br />\nwhitesugar<br />\nOX0<br />\nBlueSugar<br />\n仲用埋分身<br />\n條片入面有我真實錄音<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/kCHLTB16cAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FkCHLTB16cAg&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=fbc8f318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/kCHLTB16cAg</a><br />\n<br />\n呢啲人會喺Discord 起人底，已經頂唔信佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲會鋤埋人地舊底，再屈人，事後聲稱畀人蝦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋Google 同Discord無實際處埋<br />\ntwitter: lottery248"},{"pid":"773817280f7ae5944e7133f152b8db698fb531f7","tid":1919211,"uid":264529,"l